                  "revisionId": 2655061,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod does not increase the duration beyond the maximum duration of Cataclysm, and the added seconds do not increase the Cataclysm's size neither do they stop it from shrinking. The increased duration does however decrease the shrinking speed."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Cataclysmic Continuum",
                  "pageId": 740059,
                  "revisionId": 2655061,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The reduction of Cataclysm's radius with the augment equipped is summed up in the following formula:"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Cataclysmic Continuum",
                  "pageId": 740059,
                  "revisionId": 2655061,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Reduction = 2 × Base Radius × (1 + Range Mods) ÷ (3 × Base Duration × (1 + Duration Mods) + Augment Duration Bonus)"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Cataclysmic Continuum",
                  "pageId": 740059,
                  "revisionId": 2655061,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "While the mod does reduce the shrinking rate of Cataclysm, it does not prevent it from reaching its minimum radius, though the augment does allow players to maintain the bubble at minimum radius indefinitely as long as they kill enemies in the bubble."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Cataclysmic Continuum",
                  "pageId": 740059,
                  "revisionId": 2655061,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The effect only occurs when an enemy dies within the bubble. It still occurs when a Warframe outside the bubble kills an enemy within, but it does not occur when a Warframe within the bubble kills an enemy outside it."
                }
              }
